cies for fused silica appear\nto be in general agreement with data, where available. Predictions are made\nthat allow additional critical tests of these results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2007 16:06:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2008 21:44:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-04-25"}
